<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.1">
<l>āṟṟi liruntu viḷaiyāṭu vōṅkaḷai</l>
<l>cēṟṟā leṟintu vaḷaitukil kaikkoṇṭu</l>
<l>kāṟṟiṉ kaṭiyaṉā yōṭi yakampukku</l>
<l>māṟṟamum tārāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">vaḷaittiṟam pēcāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having thrown mud at us who were playing at the river</l>
<l>And stealing our bangles and fine clothes,</l>
<l>He entered [his] house running swiftly like the wind;</l>
<l>Because of him who won’t give [us] an answer,</l> 
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
<l>Because of him who won’t tell us where [our] bangles are,</l> 
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
